name: Amazing Princess Swimming Challenge
description:
Have a splash and get ready to dive in the amazing gymnastic swimming championship!
Be quick and get through various obstacles to get the highest score. Do ballet in the water and feel like a mermaid and be a gymnastics circulate princess. Enjoy this game with your friends and beat their high scores! This game will test your gymnastic skills and abilities in getting through various obstacles in the pool. Prove you are a champion and beat your friends high scores and be the best swimmer!

This game features:

-Challenging obstacles
-Colorful and fun graphics
-Engaging in game music
-Exciting levels
-Tons of fun
